OL,3,CMeghan and Harry hail 'reckoning' for
OL,4,Csocial media firms after US court
OL,5,Cruling
OL,7,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex
OL,8,Fwelcomed a "reckoning" for social
OL,9,Fmedia giants after a US court found
OL,10,FMeta and Google liable for a woman's
OL,11,Fchildhood social media addiction.
OL,13,FIn a potentially precedent-setting
OL,14,Fruling on Wednesday in Los Angeles, a
OL,15,Fjury ruled that Google, owner of
OL,16,FYouTube, and Meta, which operates
OL,17,FFacebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp,
OL,18,Fbuilt platforms to hook young users
OL,19,Fwithout regard for their well-being.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
