FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774537862
OL,3,CMeghan and Harry hail 'reckoning' for
OL,4,Csocial media firms after US court
OL,5,Cruling
OL,7,FThe lawsuit, brought after a young
OL,8,Fwoman argued a childhood addiction to
OL,9,Fsocial media had exacerbated her
OL,10,Fmental health issues, could influence
OL,11,Fthe outcomes of thousands of similar
OL,12,Fcases which accuse social media firms
OL,13,Fof causing harm.
OL,15,FIn a statement, the Duke and Duchess
OL,16,Fof Sussex said: "This verdict is a
OL,17,Freckoning. For too long, families have
OL,18,Fpaid the price for platforms built
OL,19,Fwith total disregard for the children
OL,20,Fthey reach.
OL,26,@xD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774537862
OL,3,CMeghan and Harry hail 'reckoning' for
OL,4,Csocial media firms after US court
OL,5,Cruling
OL,7,F"We stand with every parent and young
OL,8,Fperson who refused to be silenced.
OL,9,FToday, the truth has been heard and
OL,10,Fprecedent has been set.
OL,12,F"Let this be the change ` where our
OL,13,Fchildren's safety is finally
OL,14,Fprioritised above profit."
OL,16,FThe jury recommended the 20-year-old
OL,17,Fplaintiff be awarded 6 million dollars
OL,18,F(#4.4 million) in damages. Both Meta
OL,19,Fand Google disagreed with the verdict
OL,20,Fand confirmed they were planning to
OL,21,Fappeal.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
