OL,3,CMeghan and Harry hail 'reckoning' for
OL,4,Csocial media firms after US court
OL,5,Cruling
OL,7,FBefore the verdict was announced, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson for Meghan and Harry said
OL,9,Fthe trial had already been a "turning
OL,10,Fpoint" for big tech firms.
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "It has forced
OL,13,Fsome of the most powerful companies on
OL,14,Fearth to reveal what's behind the
OL,15,Fcurtain and to answer, in public and
OL,16,Fon the record, for choices that shaped
OL,17,Fan entire generation's daily life."
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@FO]tD@VOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
