OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774537862
OL,3,CMeghan and Harry hail 'reckoning' for
OL,4,Csocial media firms after US court
OL,5,Cruling
OL,7,FA Meta spokesperson said "teen mental
OL,8,Fhealth is profoundly complex and
OL,9,Fcannot be linked to a single app",
OL,10,Fwhile Google said the verdict
OL,11,Fmisunderstood YouTube, "which is a
OL,12,Fresponsibly built streaming platform,
OL,13,Fnot a social media site".
OL,15,FSnapchat and TikTok were also named
OL,16,Fdefendants in the lawsuit, but each
OL,17,Fsettled before the trial started.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUqD@aO]sD@XOUuD@XO]
