OL,3,CMeghan and Harry hail 'reckoning' for
OL,4,Csocial media firms after US court
OL,5,Cruling
OL,7,FThe California decision came a day
OL,8,Fafter a New Mexico jury found Meta
OL,9,Fliable under state consumer protection
OL,10,Flaw for misleading the public about
OL,11,Fthe safety of its platforms and
OL,12,Ffailing to protect children.
OL,14,FThe duke and duchess have long
OL,15,Fcampaigned to raise awareness about
OL,16,Fthe harms of social media, with Harry
OL,17,Fcriticising the "lawlessness" within
OL,18,Fthe industry in a podcast interview in
OL,19,FOctober.
OL,26,@yD@QOUyD@]O]
