OL,3,CMeghan and Harry hail 'reckoning' for
OL,4,Csocial media firms after US court
OL,5,Cruling
OL,7,FIn 2025, Harry and Meghan called for
OL,8,Fstronger protections for children
OL,9,Fonline after unveiling a memorial in
OL,10,FNew York City to young people who lost
OL,11,Ftheir lives due to the harmful effects
OL,12,Fof social media.
OL,14,FThe Sussexes' Archewell Foundation
OL,15,Fpreviously unveiled its Parents'
OL,16,FNetwork initiative as a support system
OL,17,Ffor parents of children affected by
OL,18,Fonline harm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
