OL,3,CMeghan and Harry hail 'reckoning' for
OL,4,Csocial media firms after US court
OL,5,Cruling
OL,7,FHarry, speaking at a Project Healthy
OL,8,FMinds event in New York City in
OL,9,FOctober, claimed that the digital
OL,10,Fworld has "fundamentally changed how
OL,11,Fwe experience reality".
OL,13,FHe said the digital world has
OL,14,F"fundamentally changed how we
OL,15,Fexperience reality ` young people
OL,16,Fexposed to relentless comparison,
OL,17,Fharassment, misinformation and an
OL,18,Fattention economy designed to keep us
OL,19,Fscrolling at the expense of sleep and
OL,20,Freal human contact".
